results.name: Ether255
results.description: Ether255 is a unique one-on-one game of luck where
results.fullDescription:
Ether255 is a unique one-on-one game of luck where you can win Ether through a quick and fun “compare the numbers” game. Unlike online casinos, Ether255 takes out the middlemen and each match is played directly between players as one-on-one challenges.
The game, found at Ether255.com, is based on the Ethereum blockchain and uses an Ethereum smart contract to place bets. Ether255 promises all plays to be provably fair and requires no deposits. Each wheel spin is random and cryptographically secure.
Play is very simple: each player spins the wheel and compares the result with his opponent’s. Numbers range between 0 to 255. If you win, your winnings are paid into your account immediately. The company takes a 2% commission fee.
Ether255 is straightforward and requires only a bit of luck. If you are feeling lucky, go to Ether255.com and start winning some Ether today!
